<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.9">
<l>entai tantai tammā ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟemarē ḻēḻaḷavum</l>
<l>vantu niṉṟa toṇṭa rōrkkē vāci vallīrāl</l>
<l>cintai taṉṉuḷ munti niṟṟir ciṟitun tirumēṉi</l>
<l>inta vaṇṇa meṉṟu kāṭṭī rinta ḷūrīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For servants who have kept coming for seven[-times-]</l>
<l rend="indent">seven [generations] of our people,</l>
<l>Those being my father, his father, [and] his father,</l>
<l rend="indent">you are surely one who can do what is right.</l>
<l>You remain at the fore in our thoughts; you of Intaḷūr,</l>
<l>You do not show [us] even a little that [your] divine form [is of] this nature.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
